Question
========
Wat is de ontbrekende *F-waarde *van GROEP in de ANOVA-tabel die hieronder wordt gepresenteerd? Rond af op drie decimalen.  
  

  
![](Capture12333.gif)


Solution
========

SS<sub>M</sub> / *df*<sub>M</sub> = MS<sub>M</sub> SS<sub>R</sub> / *df*<sub>R</sub> = MS<sub>R</sub> MS<sub>M</sub> / MS<sub>R</sub> = *F*  MS<sub>M</sub> = 5,624 / 3 = 1,875 MS<sub>R</sub> = 57,695 / 95 = 0,607
* * = 1.875 / .607 = 3.089
